sources.description:
A detective's desperate hunt to stop the immortal party crashers.
Detective Hank Holten (Kevin Dillon) uncovers a vampire nest preying on LA's underground rave scene. With his ex-wife Susan (Vanessa Angel) and skeptical Captain Billings (Lance Henriksen) in the crosshairs, he must stop the bloodsuckers before the city becomes an all-night buffet.
